{"tid":1485490,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"日本北陸 行程  求指點","createTime":"2019-08-18T16:05:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T07:25:02.000Z","uid":118444,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"98c75e12b4790d6b7eae499ff76f3d114817c9ad","tid":1485490,"uid":118444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:05:51.000Z","msg":"想食兩餐蟹，但又唔想連續食， 所以分左頭尾2日去<br />\n行程以舒服為主，唔走太多景點<br />\n<br />\n我應該買邊張Pass ?  <br />\n<br />\nDay 1  :  香港01:50 &gt; 關西機場 &gt;  加賀溫泉 1泊2食<br />\n<br />\nDay 2 : 加賀溫泉  &gt; 白川鄉 &gt; 高山<br />\n<br />\nDay 3 : 高山 &gt; 新穗高 &gt; 飛驒高山 &gt; 高山<br />\n<br />\nDay 4 : 高山 &gt; 福井溫泉  1泊2食  <br />\n<br />\nDay 5 : 福井 &gt; 永平寺 &gt; 京都<br />\n<br />\nDay 6 : 京都行少少景點 &gt; 香港機場<br />\n<br />\nThanks"},{"pid":"a757d4bff8a6f20af75a1a46a92986653b61bfa7","tid":1485490,"uid":201374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:26:52.000Z","msg":"自駕?"},{"pid":"1e0fff341c4358fa3040cafe07a5ffa952a2733c","tid":1485490,"uid":118444,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a757d4bff8a6f20af75a1a46a92986653b61bfa7","tid":1485490,"uid":201374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:26:52.000Z","msg":"自駕?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:43:47.000Z","msg":"唔係 阿，搭JR /巴士"},{"pid":"2cd192a68db0a7ed4d0c33efdc21df75c4bbf8d1","tid":1485490,"uid":33727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:51:22.000Z","msg":"其實你去google打 北陸Pass<br />\n第一個結果就係答案"},{"pid":"e4adf5a98b3f8c2b56d122ebe7b2142dd91d66a2","tid":1485490,"uid":201374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e0fff341c4358fa3040cafe07a5ffa952a2733c","tid":1485490,"uid":118444,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a757d4bff8a6f20af75a1a46a92986653b61bfa7","tid":1485490,"uid":201374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:26:52.000Z","msg":"自駕?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:43:47.000Z","msg":"唔係 阿，搭JR /巴士"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T02:21:25.000Z","msg":"JR+巴士嘅話其實你除咗高山、北陸地區周遊券之外應該冇乜其他選擇<br />\n新穗高嗰日建議你買＂｢奧飛騨｣まるごとバリューきっぷ＂<br />\n不過你除咗day4朝早可以行吓朝市，應該冇乜時間行高山市"},{"pid":"a3812ca437e45bb838b419b5087849544670096b","tid":1485490,"uid":47041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:14:31.000Z","msg":"福井溫泉即係邊度?"},{"pid":"528d475817771f583c2d87026e510a45a848cf5c","tid":1485490,"uid":20160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:35:27.000Z","msg":"行程ok, 新穗高係為左睇紅葉?<br />\n福井同加賀住邊間溫泉?"},{"pid":"af376a5bbaaa2c9e5515c2823290c37b8f477282","tid":1485490,"uid":201374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"528d475817771f583c2d87026e510a45a848cf5c","tid":1485490,"uid":20160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:35:27.000Z","msg":"行程ok, 新穗高係為左睇紅葉?<br />\n福井同加賀住邊間溫泉?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T08:24:58.000Z","msg":"越前蟹應該冬天先有"},{"pid":"befc5fb00057deeacb7f0390a5e681381600bc73","tid":1485490,"uid":20160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af376a5bbaaa2c9e5515c2823290c37b8f477282","tid":1485490,"uid":201374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"528d475817771f583c2d87026e510a45a848cf5c","tid":1485490,"uid":20160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:35:27.000Z","msg":"行程ok, 新穗高係為左睇紅葉?<br />\n福井同加賀住邊間溫泉?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T08:24:58.000Z","msg":"越前蟹應該冬天先有"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T08:54:41.000Z","msg":"一般黎講越前蟹都係11月頭解禁<br />\n所以就啱時間就可以紅葉 + 越前蟹一舉兩得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但要睇樓主幾時去<br />\n11月頭去可能得新穗高水尾+越前蟹+永平寺紅葉<br />\n但如果11月中, 11月尾先去就可以用其他 spot replace 新穗高<br />\n<br />\nref:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.town-echizen.jp/pages/index.php?id=9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.town-echizen.jp%2Fpages%2Findex.php%3Fid%3D9&d=T%2BmtXVGNOTzTHFJD9Tq3cTizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=d340f270\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.town-echizen.jp/pages/index.php?id=9</a>"},{"pid":"1281e7b547be280be56822e610b1a4d5177ce86a","tid":1485490,"uid":118444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4adf5a98b3f8c2b56d122ebe7b2142dd91d66a2","tid":1485490,"uid":201374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e0fff341c4358fa3040cafe07a5ffa952a2733c","tid":1485490,"uid":118444,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a757d4bff8a6f20af75a1a46a92986653b61bfa7","tid":1485490,"uid":201374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:26:52.000Z","msg":"自駕?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:43:47.000Z","msg":"唔係 阿，搭JR /巴士"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T02:21:25.000Z","msg":"JR+巴士嘅話其實你除咗高山、北陸地區周遊券之外應該冇乜其他選擇<br />\n新穗高嗰日建議你買＂｢奧飛騨｣まるごとバリューきっぷ＂<br />\n不過你除咗day4朝早可以行吓朝市，應該冇乜時間行高山市"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:07:43.000Z","msg":"想問下  高山有無車可以直到福井？"},{"pid":"e7fd96108b3360a80552373e414e2305335615b2","tid":1485490,"uid":118444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"528d475817771f583c2d87026e510a45a848cf5c","tid":1485490,"uid":20160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:35:27.000Z","msg":"行程ok, 新穗高係為左睇紅葉?<br />\n福井同加賀住邊間溫泉?"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:10:35.000Z","msg":"我新年去炸，應該睇雪景<br />\n福井住芳泉<br />\n加賀住 界 加賀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有無邊間溫泉食蟹唔錯可以推介？"},{"pid":"f8b8adc34e9b2724a9c6c031891299c262a8b209","tid":1485490,"uid":304195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:14:15.000Z","msg":"都係得高山北陸pass可以揀 包埋去白川鄉個程巴士<br />\n可以去埋金沢 由加賀出發25分鐘JR特急就到 包回本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但個pass淨係得5日 你要自己決定頭尾邊日唔用啦"},{"pid":"6b7a3840128f05010755bd2cbfddd714958b2a32","tid":1485490,"uid":20160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7fd96108b3360a80552373e414e2305335615b2","tid":1485490,"uid":118444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"528d475817771f583c2d87026e510a45a848cf5c","tid":1485490,"uid":20160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-0